item.description:
Source: TW
A thread those who don&rsquo;t know what Puri Shankaracharya ji has done. &hellip;
Do you know that the present Jagadguru Shankaracharya ji had left his home and hearth in 1960 after taking a pledge to adopt the Sanyas order at 17? It is also worth mentioning that he actively participated in the meeting held on 7 November 1966 right in front of the Indian Parliament. Even before the commencement of the above meeting, Shri Gavananda Hariji had received three hours of advice and guidance from him on the main issues of that meeting.
